just friends ? ( hangul : 친구사이 ? ; rr : chingusai ? ) is a 2009 south korean short film directed and written by kim jho kwang-soo .   it is the second installment in a series of gay-themed short films directed by kim , following the 2008 film boy meets boy .   the film stars yeon woo-jin and lee je-hoon , who together play a couple that must deal with the issue of coming out .   it premiered at the 14th pusan international film festival on october 10 , 2009 .   two months later on december 17 , just friends ?   was theatrically released in south korea .   a follow-up to just friends ?